<title>USA: Gleason sees acquistion completed in Q2.</title>
<headline>Gleason sees acquistion completed in Q2.</headline>
<dateline>ROCHESTER, N.Y. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Gleason Corp said Tuesday it expects to complete its acquisition of Hermann Pfauter Group in the second quarter.</p>
<p>&quot;We have received regulatory approval in the U.S., and while similar approval in Germany is still pending, we believe this will not delay closing on this transaction,&quot; said Gleason chairman and president James Gleason.</p>
<p>&quot;It has taken longer than originally anticipated to resolve certain remaining details with the sellers, but we expect based upon recent discussions with the sellers that agreement on these issues can be reached in the near-term.&quot;</p>
</text>
